 <text id="F3068T">
  <front id="d2">
   <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
    <p>Demus writes that he hopes to be home soon and will bring money with him.</p>
   </div1>
  </front>

  <body id="d4">
   <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
    <head>
     <name type="recipient">Mary Jane Demus</name>
    </head>

    <opener>
     <dateline>
      <date value="1864-11-28">november the 28th</date>
      <name type="place">morris Island <orig reg="South">Soth</orig>
       <abbr expan="Carolina">Car</abbr><lb/>54th <orig reg="Massachusetts">Mastues</orig>
       <orig reg="regiment">redgn</orig></name>
     </dateline>
     <salute/>
    </opener>

    <p>I <orig reg="Pleasant">Pleasent</orig> time to set <orig reg="down">dow</orig> to inform you
     that i am Well at Present and hope <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> the <orig reg="few">fu</orig>
     <orig reg="lines">lynes</orig> reach you <orig reg="they">tha</orig>
     <orig reg="may">ma</orig>
     <orig reg="find">finde</orig> you in the same state of <orig reg="health">healt</orig> i <orig
      reg="Would">Wod</orig> be <orig reg="happy">hapey</orig> to hear <orig reg="from">frum</orig>
     you and you and you <orig reg="need">nead</orig> not be <unclear>saveing</unclear>
     <orig reg="off">of</orig>
     <orig reg="your">yor</orig> money for i Will be <orig reg="home">hom</orig> in a <orig
      reg="short">sorte</orig> time and i <orig reg="don't">donte</orig>
     <orig reg="Want">Wonte</orig> you to get a <unclear>sole</unclear> if you Can <orig reg="do"
      >dow</orig>
     <orig reg="without">withe oute</orig> for i Will <orig reg="fetch">fetch</orig> you
      <unclear>Wasn</unclear> home <orig reg="When">Whean</orig> i <unclear>bum</unclear> and if you
      <unclear>bont</unclear>
     <unclear>dow</unclear> With <unclear>oru</unclear>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> you <orig reg="may">ma</orig> get <orig reg="One">Wan</orig>
     <orig reg="but">bute</orig> but <orig reg="don't">dont</orig> pay too <orig reg="much"
     >mach</orig> for it <orig reg="for">fer</orig> i <unclear>ges</unclear>
     <unclear>thar</unclear>
     <orig reg="are">ar</orig> hi <unclear>thar</unclear> and if you <orig reg="Can't">Cant</orig>
     get <orig reg="One">Wone</orig>
     <orig reg="Why">Wiy</orig> let me <orig reg="know">now</orig> nothing <orig reg="more"
     >mor</orig> at present but still <orig reg="remain">reman</orig></p>

    <closer>
     <salute><orig reg="your">yor</orig> Dear <orig reg="husband">husben</orig></salute>
     <signed>David <orig reg="Demus">Demes</orig> to Marrey Jane Demus</signed>
    </closer>
   </div1>
  </body>
